THIRD-PARTY DATA LICENCES
==========================

This repository uses the following publicly available datasets. Their use is
governed by the terms specified by their respective providers:

1. Berkeley Earth Surface Temperature (BEST)
   Source  : https://berkeleyearth.org/data/
   Licence : Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
   Citation: Rohde, R.A. & Hausfather, Z. (2020). The Berkeley Earth land/
             ocean temperature record. Earth Syst. Sci. Data 12, 3469–3479.
             https://doi.org/10.5194/essd-12-3469-2020

2. NOAA Mauna Loa Atmospheric CO₂ Concentration (Keeling Curve)
   Source  : https://gml.noaa.gov/ccgg/trends/
   Licence : Public Domain / US Government Open Data
   Citation: NOAA Global Monitoring Laboratory (2025). Trends in Atmospheric
             Carbon Dioxide. https://gml.noaa.gov/ccgg/trends/

3. SILSO International Sunspot Number V2.0
   Source  : https://www.sidc.be/silso/datafiles
   Licence : Creative Commons Attribution–Non-Commercial 4.0 (CC BY-NC 4.0)
   Citation: Clette, F. & Lefèvre, L. (2015). SILSO Sunspot Number V2.0.
             WDC-SILSO, Royal Observatory of Belgium.
             https://doi.org/10.24414/qnza-ac80

Please ensure compliance with each dataset's licence when redistributing or
publishing work derived from this repository.
